high_descs: Walk forward and turn to the counter on your right.
Pick up the mug from the counter.
Turn to the right and walk until you get to the microwave.
Warm the cup in the microwave, then pull it out again.
Turn around, then turn right, and walk until you get to the wooden shelf.
Place the mug on the top shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place a warmed mug on a shelf.

high_descs: Move to the left and stand in front of the counter near the white mug.
Pick the white mug up from the counter.
Go right and stand in front of the microwave.
Put the mug in the microwave, turn it on and then take the mug out and shut the door.
Go left and stand in front of the brown shelves.
Put the cup down on the shelf in the middle of the top shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a warmed mug on a shelf.

high_descs: look left, and then return to your starting position
take the coffee mug from the counter
turn right and go forward to the stove. Turn to face the stove, then look up at the microwave
Open the microwave door, and place the mug in the microwave. Close the door. Heat the mug in the microwave for 3 seconds, then remove it and close the microwave door.
Look back to your normal elevation, then turn around, move slightly towards the counter, turn right, and head to the far wall. Then, turn right and head to the shelf.
Place the mug on the top shelf, next to the credit card.
anns.task_desc: Place a warm mug on the top shelf.
